      About this item

      • 3-in-1 Fingerprint Door Lock: Our advanced smart lock have 3 unlocking methods, including fingerprint identification, app control, and mechanical key, so you can choose the unlocking method according to your needs and preferences, and experience the unparalleled convenience and security of smart door knob
      • Smart Notifications: This smart door lock has a voice feedback function, which can give voice alerts based on your actions, such as locking, unlocking, operating fail, etc., You can also invite others to become family members through the APP, share access rights with family members, and view real-time fingerprint door lock status and receive instant alerts. Every time someone picks the lock or the door is opened, you will receive instant alerts
      • Enhanced Security: This fingerprint door lock is equipped with a biometric fingerprint sensor that recognizes your finger in 0.2s and can store up to 50 fingerprints. fingerprint door knob can be set to auto lock in 5-60s, fingerprint door lock with auto lock, one touch locking, passage mode and low battery alarm function, one-touch door opening function can ensure your home security
      • Durable & Easy Installation: The smart door lock with handle requires 4 AAA batteries (not included), the battery life of the electronic door lock is up to 1 year, our door locks with fingerprints are IP54 waterproof rated for house, front door, bedroom, apartment, office, hotel, no matter inside or outdoor. It is easy to install and requires only a screwdriver, package included detailed installation manaul and technical support to facilitate the replacement of your door lock
      • Service Guarantee: This door lock comes with 30 days return service

      Previous page
      Next page

      • What type of door is this door knob suitable for?

        The smart door knob is suitable for wooden or steel doors with a thickness of 34-55 mm.

      • App couldn't find my door lock, what should I do?

        Please ensure the batteries have installed in the door knob, then reset the lock by pressing the setting button on the interior knob. you will hear a voice prompt“Please add Bluetooth Administrator“, then connect to the APP via Bluetooth.

      • How can I manually lock (without the app) from the inside.

        You can turn on privacy mode, in privacy mode only the administrator's fingerprint can open the lock, which can be done by following steps.

        ON: Under locking state, long press the reset button for 2s.

        OFF: Shortly press the button to turn it off.

      • How can l remotely unlock it? Do l need a gateway device to use this lock？

        The door lock allows you to control your door when there is no gateway. If you are not at home, you will need to purchase a tuya smart gateway for remote control

      • How do I keep the door unlocked?

        In the unlocked state, long press the reset button for 2 seconds or turn off the auto lock function in the APP. (Tip: Reset button on interior door knob)

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      • Misha
        5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent lock
        Reviewed in the United States on July 14, 2024
        Verified Purchase
        I recently purchased the Smart Door Lock, and overall, I am quite impressed with its performance and features. This advanced door lock offers the convenience of keyless entry, multiple user access, and enhanced security..

        Design and Build Quality

        The Smart Door Lock boasts a sleek and modern design that seamlessly blends with various door styles. Its robust build quality feels solid and durable, giving confidence in its ability to withstand daily use and potential tampering. The keypad is illuminated, making it easy to use even in low-light conditions.

        Installation

        Installation was straightforward and hassle-free. The lock came with a detailed instruction manual and all necessary hardware. I was able to fit it to my door without requiring professional assistance, although those less handy might prefer some help. The process took about 30-45 minutes.

        Features and Functionality

        Fingerprint Recognition:
        One of the standout features is the fingerprint recognition system. Adding fingerprints is done through the companion app, which is intuitive and user-friendly. The app guides you through the process of adding and managing multiple users. I found the fingerprint scanner to be highly accurate and responsive, recognizing registered prints almost instantly.

        App Integration:
        The smart lock is integrated with a dedicated mobile app available for both iOS and Android. Through the app, you can add or remove fingerprints and monitor lock activity. The app also sends real-time notifications for any lock or unlock actions, enhancing security by keeping you informed of who is accessing your door.

        Battery Life:
        The lock requires batteries to operate. Make sure to insert new batteries with full battery life. Mine, although new, were purchased a couple years back and the app shows you how much life the battery got which is very convenient. Mine are not doing so well. Also, the lock will not lock if your batteries are almost at zero.

        Security Features:
        The lock includes several security features such as anti-peep PIN entry, where you can enter random digits before or after your actual PIN to prevent onlookers from guessing your code. The lock also has a built-in alarm that triggers if someone attempts to tamper with it or if the wrong fingerprint/PIN is entered multiple times.

        Performance

        In daily use, the Smart Door Lock performs reliably. The fingerprint recognition is swift, and I have not encountered any issues with the app or the locking mechanism. The physical lock itself feels sturdy, and the motorized locking mechanism operates smoothly.
